Project Description
DeviantDOCK is a luancher which organizes your shortcut file, folder in you desktop. Obviously you can use and change animation, skins and position too. All you need is just select any icon and choose its location and then save it. This also supports drag & drop feature too.

System Requirements:

1. Windows Vista/7
2. .Net Framework 3.0 (minimum, comes with Windows by default).
